channel.title: Luring Clan. MoparLure
channel.description:
This is a clan for luring. I myself have DClaws on an account, and am getting other high hit weapons. We will be luring via the new clan wars type thing. (For some odd reason I cannot remember the name.). We will be finding higher level (Good armour people.)
We may also use a sort of trade and get money lure, having people waiting in the wilderness. I have done this lure before. FOR BOTH OF THESE, we need: farcaster with ice barrage, and someone who will have the money and be "giving" it to our members.
For this we need a pure of some sort that is low level. I do not have this account, we need someone. We will find a target, then someone will lure them (We will be giving this account 40m or something, and we have a tactic that works, will share.). To be in this clan, you MUST be a member, we are not doing ftp luring.
If you would like to join apply below using this format: RSN: (You may pm this if you don't want to share). Reason: Level: Wealth And Armour/Weapons: What style do you use(farcast, dbow, spec, etc.): Info that may help us, such as if you are a pure, if you have cash that is just sitting their, rares, etc.
Thanks for reading, I am looking forward to Luring with fellow Moparians.
